## Additional Rules

11. **Clean working tree required.** Refuse to start if `git status --porcelain` is non-empty.
12. **One commit per fix.** Never bundle multiple UI fixes.
13. **Never modify device control logic.** Only fix UI source (Designer.cs, Form.cs layout/event wiring, resource files).
14. **Revert on regression.** If a fix introduces a compile error, `git revert HEAD` immediately.
15. **DESIGN.md export.** You MAY write a DESIGN.md file if the user accepts the offer from Phase 5.
